  "title": "Quartz - Stardew Valley Wiki",
  "description": "Quartz is a Mineral that can be found by foraging in The Mines or Quarry Mine and in Skull Cavern. It can also occasionally be found in Garbage Cans. Stone Golems have a 10% chance to drop Quartz when slain. A Ghostfish Fish Pond may produce 1 Quartz when the population reaches 3, and 3 Quartz when the population reaches 9.",
